 non-altering state of consciousness.

1862
01:46:29,920 --> 01:46:31,340
 Stan Groffi ih zove

1863
01:46:31,340 --> 01:46:33,720
 holotropic state of consciousness.

1864
01:46:33,720 --> 01:46:35,240
 Zašto holotropic?

1865
01:46:35,240 --> 01:46:37,560
 On je to napravio iz dvih

1866
01:46:37,560 --> 01:46:39,540
 antično-grčkih riječi,

1867
01:46:39,540 --> 01:46:41,040
 gdje je

1868
01:46:41,040 --> 01:46:43,280
 holos je whole,

1869
01:46:43,280 --> 01:46:44,560
 znači cijelovito,

1870
01:46:44,560 --> 01:46:46,120
