 kad sam bila mala.

1883
01:47:10,680 --> 01:47:13,460
 Ja nisam imala to iskustvo,

1884
01:47:13,460 --> 01:47:15,280
 ali taj primjer je tako lijepo svikovit.

1885
01:47:15,280 --> 01:47:17,500
 I sad, jer to je bilo

1886
01:47:17,500 --> 01:47:19,420
 toliko traumatično da sam ja to

1887
01:47:19,420 --> 01:47:21,460
 potisnula negdje u svoje

1888
01:47:21,460 --> 01:47:22,700
 podsvjesno ili nesvjesno,

1889
01:47:22,700 --> 01:47:25,100
 na način da ili uopće se ne sjećam

1890
01:47:25,100 --> 01:47:26,320
 da sam imala to iskustvo,

1891
01:47:26,320 --> 01:47:28,680
