1892
01:47:28,680 --> 01:47:30,500
 Ali mene je na smrt

1893
01:47:30,500 --> 01:47:33,360
 strah vode, a kamo li duboke vode.

1894
01:47:33,360 --> 01:47:35,280
 To me ograničava u životu.

1895
01:47:35,560 --> 01:47:37,020
 Ne mogu i čjedriti jer se bojem

1896
01:47:37,020 --> 01:47:37,980
