1897
01:47:37,980 --> 01:47:40,140
 Bojem se plivati daleko,

1898
01:47:40,140 --> 01:47:41,780
 a plivala bi jer volim plivati.

1899
01:47:41,780 --> 01:47:45,820
 I sad, ako u ovakvom nekom procesu

1900
01:47:45,820 --> 01:47:48,280
 moja unutarnja mudrost

1901
01:47:48,280 --> 01:47:50,420
 donese to na površinu,

1902
01:47:50,420 --> 01:47:52,600
 da ja mogu prvo osvijestiti to

1903
01:47:52,600 --> 01:47:55,240
 i onda proći kroz te emocije

1904
